This code enables you to solve any maze which is given in the form of a matrix of 1's and 0's where, 1 represents a wall and 0 represents a path

maze.py
This is the main file. This has to be run.

Graphics.py 
This file is imported in Maze.py and it generates the GUI for the maze.

PLay.py 
This file gets the input from the maze.py file, regarding which cell has been visited, the coordinates are sent to the play.py file 
which plays the tune for every tile. 

Databse.py
This file fetches the maze from the database and gives it to maze.py which in turn uses graphics.py file to generate the GUI of the maze.
Further  if any new maze is given by the user, then it  is stored in the database
